Code Operation:
Add Book: Allows you to add a new book to the system.
List Books: Displays all registered books with their details.
Search Book: Allows you to search for books by title or author.
Remove Book: Removes a book by ID.
Exit: Closes the program.

New Features Added:
Add Movie: Allows you to add a new movie to the system.
List Movies: Displays all registered movies with their details.
Search Movie: Allows you to search for movies by title or director.
Remove Movie: Removes a movie by ID.